stories_text_raw:
As a system administrator, I want to process deletions for a given date, so that I can manage the system's data effectively.
As a developer, I want to redesign the Resources page, so that it matches the new Broker design styles and provides a better user experience.
As a tester, I want to report user testing results to Agencies, so that stakeholders can track progress and identify areas for improvement.
As a content creator, I want to move on to the next round of edits for a given page, so that I can refine and improve the content.
As a troubleshooter, I want to log better for troubleshooting issues with submissions and functions, so that I can quickly identify and resolve problems.
As a data manager, I want to update the FABS sample file, so that it is up-to-date and accurate.
As a data quality specialist, I want to ensure deleted FSRS records are not included in submissions, so that the data remains accurate and reliable.
As a validation expert, I want to update the Broker validation rule table, so that it reflects the latest rules and guidelines.
As a database administrator, I want to add GTAS window data to the database, so that the system can enforce the necessary restrictions.
As a performance optimizer, I want to manage D Files generation requests, so that the system can handle the workload efficiently.
As a data analyst, I want to access raw agency published files from FABS via USAspending, so that I can analyze and gain insights from the data.
As a developer, I want to include a large number of flexfields, so that the system can handle complex and varied data.
As a designer, I want to create content mockups, so that I can visualize and test the layout and design of the content.
